398
00:15:14,679 --> 00:15:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, Bog nas želi preobraziti

399
00:15:17,340 --> 00:15:19,159
[SPEAKER_00] na sliku svoju.

400
00:15:19,159 --> 00:15:20,820
[SPEAKER_00] I to je hod,

401
00:15:20,820 --> 00:15:22,399
[SPEAKER_00] svakodnevni hod

402
00:15:22,399 --> 00:15:24,080
[SPEAKER_00] k svetosti

403
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:25,179
[SPEAKER_00] na koju smo pozvani.

404
00:15:25,179 --> 00:15:28,139
[SPEAKER_00] K ljubavi na koju smo pozvani.

405
00:15:28,139 --> 00:15:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] Kako da ja ljubim tebe

406
00:15:29,500 --> 00:15:31,059
[SPEAKER_00] ako nisam ljubila sebe?

407
00:15:31,059 --> 00:15:32,740
[SPEAKER_00] Kako da ja volim tebe,

408
00:15:32,740 --> 00:15:34,139
[SPEAKER_00] imam strpljenja za tebe,

409
00:15:34,139 --> 00:15:35,659
[SPEAKER_00] nema šanse.

410
00:15:35,659 --> 00:15:36,919
[SPEAKER_00] A danas?

411
00:15:36,919 --> 00:15:38,600
[SPEAKER_00] Danas imam strpljenja

412
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:39,700
[SPEAKER_00] i tekako

413
00:15:39,700 --> 00:15:40,940
[SPEAKER_00] i danas može Bog

414
00:15:40,940 --> 00:15:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] mene upotrijebiti za druge.

415
00:15:42,460 --> 00:15:45,799
[SPEAKER_00] Prije me ne prijatelj upotrijebio

416
00:15:45,799 --> 00:15:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] da torpediram druge,

417
00:15:47,159 --> 00:15:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] da ih povrijedim,

418
00:15:48,559 --> 00:15:50,679
[SPEAKER_00] da im kažem šta god mi dođe,

419
00:15:51,259 --> 00:15:52,679
[SPEAKER_00] a danas me Bog upotrijebi

420
00:15:52,679 --> 00:15:53,919
[SPEAKER_00] da ohrabrim druge.

421
00:15:53,919 --> 00:15:55,059
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

422
00:15:55,059 --> 00:15:57,399
[SPEAKER_00] važnost rada na sebi

423
00:15:57,399 --> 00:15:58,860
[SPEAKER_00] je i u tome

424
00:15:58,860 --> 00:16:00,720
[SPEAKER_00] da ako se ja mijenjam,

425
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:02,340
[SPEAKER_00] mene promijenjenu Bog

426
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] može upotrijebiti

427
00:16:03,340 --> 00:16:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] na blagoslov crkvi

428
00:16:04,539 --> 00:16:05,919
[SPEAKER_00] i narodu Božjem.

429
00:16:05,919 --> 00:16:06,940
[SPEAKER_00] Meni samoj,

430
00:16:06,940 --> 00:16:07,620
[SPEAKER_00] ali i vama.

431
00:16:07,620 --> 00:16:09,799
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, Niko.

432
00:16:09,799 --> 00:16:10,240
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

433
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:11,600
[SPEAKER_00] viš da mogu završiti ta vijena.

434
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:13,360
[SPEAKER_00] Sačo moru.

435
00:16:15,360 --> 00:16:18,779
[UNKNOWN] Hvala što pratite.

436
00:16:18,779 --> 00:16:20,580
[UNKNOWN] Hvala što pratite.

